{"tid":712339,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【月初亞視裁員】TVBI兩經理級職員離職 傳TVB派大信封","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T15:46:08.000Z","uid":17646,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f263e170913689ce096d8bce01dbff6306de8e79","tid":712339,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"亞視今年1月尾先以OTT平台復活，但本月初亞視對外事務部總監曾醒明其後又證實，有約30人離職，連「顧問」吳雨及區偉林都「友好地」解除合約，上星期亞視首席「內容官」（CCO）何麗全就話會喺8月請番人。（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K8M2I5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2K8M2I5&d=%2BRw2xM0Hd4f155oiEcL3Q6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=90dab9a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2K8M2I5</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n點知一波未平，一波又起，呢次唔係亞視，而係香港人睇慣睇熟嘅TVB有動作&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n今日facebook page「方以文 睇電視喇喂」，指出TVB近日裁員，受影響嘅包括TVBI同Broadcast Operation Department，收「大信封」嘅人數，佔咗部門總人數10%。<br />\n<br />\n據知，TVBI現時部門職員數目約有50至100人，最近的確有兩位經理級職員離職，亦有消息指，TVBI最近有新高層入主，或會重整部門架構，至於是否陸續有來則屬未知之數。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180621/large/1529595291_5d91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180621%2Flarge%2F1529595291_5d91.jpg&h=9dad98ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4c090ebf2193addf82a990b92f5844f4a8046dd","tid":712339,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf6abed98547f72cf0de292c3d1fc7142abd9b0","tid":712339,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc5f363959441da72a2b7082eac6bc7b92286ce","tid":712339,"uid":77467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eaf6abed98547f72cf0de292c3d1fc7142abd9b0","tid